OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCall to ban 'forced' switch
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto prepayment meters       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Citizens Advice has called for a ban on
OL,6, energy companies "forcing" customers   
OL,7, onto prepayment meters because they are
OL,8, struggling to pay bills.               
OL,10,FThe charity estimates that 600,000     
OL,11,Fpeople were put onto the pay-as-you-go 
OL,12,Fmethod last year, with 160,000 more    
OL,13,Fexpected by the end of the winter.     
OL,15,FSome have meters installed, while      
OL,16,Fothers have smart meters automatically 
OL,17,Fswitched to prepayment mode.           
OL,19,FLast year, regulator Ofgem wrote to    
OL,20,Fsuppliers about the issue.             
